OL,3,CCould one of the UK's most iconic
OL,4,Cpebble beaches be replaced with sand?
OL,6,FIt's one of the UK's most iconic
OL,7,Fpebble beaches, but calls have been
OL,8,Fmade to transform Brighton into a
OL,9,Fsandy beach, echoing the dunes of
OL,10,FCamber Sands.
OL,12,FSparking a debate amongst hundreds of
OL,13,Flocals, one resident described the
OL,14,Fsandy beach as 'the only thing
OL,15,FBrighton is missing.'
OL,17,FBrighton's shingle beach stretches for
OL,18,F5.4 miles and has a flat sandy
OL,19,Fforeshore which becomes exposed at low
OL,20,Ftide.
