OL,3,CCould one of the UK's most iconic
OL,4,Cpebble beaches be replaced with sand?
OL,6,F"Definitely sand, because it's more
OL,7,Feasier to walk on, on the beach. So if
OL,8,Fit's, if it's bobbly, it's just, it's
OL,9,Fjust more difficult, even with the
OL,10,Ftrainers."
OL,12,FAnother resident added: "What actually
OL,13,Fmatters to me is, like, the
